  * Diploma or Degree in Computer Science / Information Technology or business Systems 
  * 2-3 yearsâ€™ experience in a similar Service Desk or Help Desk role, providing L1/L2support 
  * Experience with industry standard Service Desk management solutions, e.g., ServiceNow, Jira, Freshdesk 
  * Excellent communication skills and the ability to build strong relationships with both internal and external clients, in person and over the phone. 
  * The ability to work autonomously and collaboratively within a small team environment. 
  * Passionate about delivering high quality IT support to customers and be willing to further develop your skills to assist you in achieving this goal. 
  * You will be a positive team player, who has flexibility, energy, initiative and a "can do" attitude, who values open communication and rapport-building with clients. 
  * Ability to manage significant workloads in a busy environment. 
  * Full working rights in Australia 

** Desirable: **

  * Experience in Logistics (TMS) and Warehouse (WMS) applications. 
  * A strong working knowledge of Microsoft technologies including O365, Teams and SharePoint. 
  * Knowledge of JAIX would be an advantage. 

